MENU_PKG_POSTGRESQL
  Within this menu you will be able to change certain config options of
  the PostgreSQL package.

SDECFG_PKG_POSTGRESQL_PREFIX
  This option defines the installation prefix of the PostgreSQL package.

  Default: opt/postgresql

SDECFG_PKG_POSTGRESQL_CONTRIB
  This option defines if the contributed 3rd. Party Applications included
  within the PostgreSQL package should be build and installed.

  Default: Yes
